translated: Öberg, Lars Harald, provincial doctor, Skene, b. 15/7/90 in Agnetorp, Ska-rab. 1st son of estate owner Carl Ö. and Frida Andersson. Mar. 21 with Stina Svensson. Children: Lars b. 22, Anders b. 26, Brita b. 3il. — Secondary school graduate in Karlstad 09, medical candidate 1-5, medical licentiate 21 at Karolinska Institute. Assistant doctor at Vadstena hospital 18-19, junior doctor at Målilla sanatorium 21-22, acting junior doctor at Karls'hamn hospital 22 and 23, assistant doctor at Sahlgr. hospital surgical department 22-23, provincial doctor and local medical officer in Högsäter district 23-32, acting junior doctor in Vänersborg in 28, provincial doctor in Skene district since 32. Communal counselor in Högsäter 29-32, chairman of the Örby parish health committee 32-38.
